msgid ""
"a) The Club has a bar where players can grab something to eat between games or have a beer.<br/>\n"
"            It can be accessed in\n"
"            <strong>\n"
"                <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Point of Sales &gt; Bar </font><font class=\"text-black\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">and contains some basic products.</span></font>\n"
"            </strong>\n"
"            <br/>\n"
"            Customers can pay by through different means, including by adding the note to their account."
msgstr ""
"ກ) ສະໂມສອນມີບາທີ່ຜູ້ຫຼິ້ນສາມາດຊື້ຂອງກິນລະຫວ່າງເກມ ຫຼື ດື່ມເບຍໄດ້.<br/>\n"
"            ເຊິ່ງສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງໄດ້ໃນ\n"
"            <strong>\n"
"                <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ໜ້າຮ້ານ (Point of Sales) &gt; "
"Bar </font><font class=\"text-black\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">ແລ"
"ະ ມີສິນຄ້າພື້ນຖານບາງຢ່າງ.</span></font>\n"
"            </strong>\n"
"            <br/>\n"
"            ລູກຄ້າສາມາດຊຳລະເງິນໄດ້ຜ່ານຫຼາຍຊ່ອງທາງ, ລວມທັງການລົງບັນທຶກໄວ້ໃນບັນຊີຂອງພວກເຂົາ."

